configset GLOBAL default_language = VALUE
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Default Value: en
Data Type    : string
Variable Type: language
Apply to List: both regular lists and the GLOBAL pseudo-list
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =

EXAMPLE:
configset GLOBAL default_language = en

(text above is from configshow, Mj2 0.1199902200, extracted 12 Apr 1999)


This sets the default language for the list (or the installation).
This is overridable by the user in several ways.  Note that at this
time this is barely implemented.  (Only English messages are supported
at the moment.)

For a list of all help topics send this one-line message
   help topics
to the server at $MJ
